強制要求選民在搬 遷後向選舉事務處更新<br />\n主要住址。只要在申請登記時提供 的主要住址是真確的，<br />\n即使在搬遷後未有更新住址，並不 屬提供虛假資料，亦沒<br />\n有違法。只要選民在登記册的紀錄 沒有被取消，其名字仍<br />\n載列在正式選民登記册上，則已搬 遷的選民仍可在其登記<br />\n住址所屬的區議會選區投票。[ 2019 年 9 月 新 增 ]</em>"},{"pid":"410c73021aa4a9bb5b144f43f0a29c5c35eb2b0f","tid":2069157,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T08:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f73e360ad75371510b97824e3e68ff2478a004d","tid":2069157,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e0c2ffffd911e650d3efd59001753776a84071ae","tid":2069157,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:42:34.000Z","msg":"簡易方法網上查閱自己是否新登記/已登記選民<br />\n<br />\n選民資料網上查閱系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">LINK：</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/welcome.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2Fwelcome.jsp&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHk%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=1407782a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/welcome.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">步驟：</span><br />\n只需輸入<br />\n（1）身份證號碼<br />\n（2）英文名/中文名/中文電碼<br />\n（3）圖片内驗證碼<br />\n（4）回答身份確認問題(地址資料，如屋苑、單位號碼)<br />\n即可查詢選民資料</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}